---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section style="padding-top: 60px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <span class="tag">Legal</span>
            <h1>Terms &amp; <span class="highlight">Conditions</span></h1>
            <p style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Effective Date: June 2026</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 40px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <h2>Terms of Use</h2>
            <p>By accessing or using this platform, you agree to the following terms.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Nature of Content</h2>
            <p>All content published on this platform is provided for informational and educational purposes. The purpose of this platform is to explore systems, structures, patterns, and mechanisms across different domains of reality.</p>
            <p><strong style="color: var(--text);">Nothing on this website should be interpreted as professional, legal, financial, medical, or other regulated advice.</strong></p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">No Guarantees</h2>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li>No outcomes are promised.</li>
                <li>No results are guaranteed.</li>
                <li>Understanding a system does not ensure success.</li>
                <li>Implementation, execution, timing, and circumstances remain outside the control of this platform.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Interpretation Responsibility</h2>
            <p>Content is structured for clarity and understanding. Interpretation, application, and decision-making remain the responsibility of the reader.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>Use of this platform is at your own discretion. No responsibility is assumed for decisions, actions, losses, damages, or outcomes resulting from the use of this website or its content.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Limitations of Knowledge</h2>
            <p>This platform operates within defined epistemic limits. Not all variables are visible. Not all outcomes can be predicted. All models, frameworks, and explanations are subject to revision as understanding evolves.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Misuse</h2>
            <p>Misinterpretation, selective reading, removal of context, or extraction of isolated concepts may lead to incorrect conclusions. This platform is not responsible for such use.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>Unless otherwise stated, all content published on this platform belongs to LucentHindu. Unauthorized reproduction, redistribution, or commercial use is not permitted without permission.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">External Links</h2>
            <p>This website may contain links to external resources or websites. LucentHindu is not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of external sites.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Changes</h2>
            <p>Content and policies may evolve over time. Any updates will be reflected on this page.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Contact</h2>
            <p>For questions regarding these terms, please use the contact methods available through this website.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>